<div class="title-divs" class="col">
	<h1 class="h1-title-text">About Us</h1>

	<h2>Our Mission</h2>
	<p>
		Our mission is to give confidence to children with disabilities, making a lasting impact on their physical and mental health, 
		and overall wellness.
		<br>
		<br>
		“Constant care for all, by all" weighs on our minds along with our slogan,
		“Never say never”.
	</p>

	<h2>Who Skate Therapy is for</h2>
	<p>
		Skate Therapy is a program for people of all ages with mental and cognitive disabilities. Our passionate volunteer staff brings 
		this group to the ice in a positive, social, and invigorating environment. 
		Our program is designed to inspire condidence and positivity, 
		and to promote a healthy lifestyle for this very special group of people.
	</p>

	<h2>Our Team</h2>
	<p>
		Each class session is very special to us, and we look forward to meeting all interested parties for whom
		this program would benefit.   
		<br>
		<br>
		We look forward to meeting you!
		<br>
		<br>
		The Skate Therapy Team
	</p>
